title: New
description: Ce panel permet de voir ceci avec cela

title: Comparing
request: SELECT name as Nom, count(*) as NB, now() as time FROM logs WHERE activity_class = 'Système'  group by name order by 2 desc limit 5

title: Global View
request: SELECT Time(timestamp)  as 'Hour', SUBSTRING(content, 1, 20) as 'Act.', SUBSTRING(name, 1, 20) as 'Tool', TIME_FORMAT(dur, '%H:%i:%s') as 'Duration' FROM logs WHERE log_type = 'keystrokes' and activity_class='Information-Documentation' order by timestamp

title: More comparison
request: SELECT   timestamp AS time, count(*) nb_actions FROM logs WHERE   $__timeFilter(timestamp)   GROUP by time ORDER BY timestamp

title: Percent of people like this
request: SELECT st_name, count(*), now() as time FROM logs WHERE activity_class = 'Système'  group by name order by 2 desc limit 5

title: Chances of success
request: SELECT  now() AS time,  chances FROM lada_predict

title: Prediction Quality
request: SELECT  now() AS time,  quality FROM lada_predict

title: The prediction seems
request: SELECT  now() AS time,   quality FROM lada_predict

title: The chance of success of the student is ...
request: SELECT  now() AS time,   chances FROM lada_predict

title: Course results
request: SELECT code, title, grade, year, status FROM lada_student_courses ORDER BY code

title: Advancement rate
request: SELECT concat(title, ' (',code, ')'), achieved*100/plan as percent FROM lada_student_courses ORDER BY code

title: Grade comparison
request: select * from  (SELECT id student , grade  FROM at41.lada_students_grades) a  CROSS JOIN (SELECT  id thestudent , grade thegrade  FROM at41.lada_students_grades where id=19) b

title: Comparative grades
request: SELECT title, student_skills, similar_student_skills, course_skills FROM lada_student_courses

title: Student's skills
request: SELECT title, student_skills, course_skills FROM lada_student_courses limit 5

title: Similar Students' skills
request: SELECT title, similar_student_skills, course_skills FROM lada_student_courses limit 5
